UserOptionDefinition.Device_PopUpDialog_V2_C.Description.Desc: Defines what text you want to appear in the main body of the dialog. Use {playername} to dynamically include the name of the player viewing the dialog, and <cr> to include a line break.

UserOptionDefinition.Device_PopUpDialog_V2_C.EnabledDuringPha: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. Pre-Game includes all phases prior to the Game starting (the waiting for players lobby on Featured Islands and the Game Start Countdown).
